Introduction
============

Annex-check is a Perl script for checking for files that would be lost if the
current remote was taken out of the annex.


Installation
============

Edit the Makefile install path variables, and do
	% make install


Usage
=====

annex-check [OPTION] TARGET

Options:
  -h --help --usage
	Print help
  -r --recursive
	If target is a directory, search files from directories recursively
  -v --verbose
	Be verbose
  -V --version
	Print annex-check version


